{"tid":752792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★無現金概念炒作嚴重　中國央行規定商戶不得拒收現金","createTime":"2018-07-23T05:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T05:50:17.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2351bd6766a61943adbf5dea5bad54b8a83582f4","tid":752792,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:47:27.000Z","msg":"手機付款在中國相當普及，基本上只要拿着手機，生活上也不需要拿出現金來付款。不過同時因為這個原因，一些商戶為了方便反而拒收現金，為不使用手機的人帶來不便。因此中國央行最近就發出公告，規定商戶不得拒收現金。<br />\n<br />\n據中國人民銀行的公告指，除法定範圍外，任何商家、單位和個人不得以格式條款、通知、聲明、告示等方式拒收現金，但依法應當使用非現金支付的情形除外。此外，銀行業金融機構、非銀行支付機構，不得要求或者誘導其他單位和個人，拒收或採歧視性措施排斥現金。除此之外，亦<span style=\"color: red;\">嚴禁業者炒作「無現金」概念</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.pro/2018/07/16/china-central-bank-says-cannot-refuse-discriminate-against-cash-payments/news/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.pro%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2Fchina-central-bank-says-cannot-refuse-discriminate-against-cash-payments%2Fnews%2F&d=7PxwOGkTbeXZjwJBTQNWwdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=7ad42fd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.pro/2018/07/16/china-central-bank-says-cannot-refuse-discriminate-against-cash-payments/news/</a>"},{"pid":"30e5c41498298df0344d868f7b477b5873da41d7","tid":752792,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8417512363139b7723460022fac4b0f461489848","tid":752792,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30e5c41498298df0344d868f7b477b5873da41d7","tid":752792,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:50:17.000Z","msg":"No IT <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}